data.description: GREAT HOME IN A GREAT LOCATION OF THE TOWN OF WINKELMAN. HOME IS IN A CUL-DE-SAC WHICH IS ADJACENT TO THE HOME OF THE 2023 1A HAYDEN HIGH SCHOOL BASEBALL CHAMPS BASEBALL FIELD. ACROSS THE STREET TO ELEMENTARY, JR HIGH AND HIGH SCHOOL. HOME FEATURES 3 BEDROOMS, 2 FULL BATHROOMS, OPEN FLOOR PLAN WITH GREAT ROOM, EAT IN KITCHEN WITH ALL APPLIANCES INCLUDED: GAS RANGE, REFRIGERATOR, FULL SIZE WASHER AND DRYER. NEW AC INSTALLED IN 2023, WELL CARED FOR HOME AND IS PRICED TO SELL. READY FOR MOVE IN. THIS ONE WON'T LAST. CLOSE TO RESTAURANTS, GROCERY STORE, POST OFFICE,MOUNTAINS, RIVERS & STREAMS. WELCOME HOME! PROPERTY IS 1 HR OUTSIDE OF TUCSON, AZ AND 1.5 HRS OUTSIDE OF MESA, AZ.
